    h1.bd-title#content Select UI (Select2)
    p.bd-lead Select2 gives you a customizable select box with support for searching, tagging, remote data sets, infinite scrolling, and many other highly used options.

    h2#getting-started Getting Started
    p 
        | Select2 was designed to be a replacement for the standard 
        code.highlighter-rouge select
        | box that is displayed by the browser. By default it supports all options and operations that are available in a standard select box, but with added flexibility.
    p Select2 can take a regular select box like this...
    .bd-example
