    h2#appearance Appearance
    p The appearance of your Select2 controls can be customized via the standard HTML attributes for 
        code.highlighter-rouge select 
        | elements

    h3#disabling-a-select2-control Disabling a Select2 control
    p 
        | Select2 will respond to the 
        code.highlighter-rouge disabled 
        | attribute on 
        code.highlighter-rouge select 
        | elements. You can also initialize Select2 with 
        code.highlighter-rouge disabled: true 
        | to get the same effect.

    .bd-example
        +selectui-disabled('select3','Select an option')
            +option("Alaska","AK")
            +option("Hawaii","HI")

